      "content": "the doctors already tried everything. there's nothing left to do. it's just... it's just life now. a lifetime of this. every day is just a cycle of pain and trying to distract myself so i dont scream. it feels so cruel that this is all there is left for me. it would be so much kinder if everything just went quiet. if i could just find some peace and not have to wake up to this anymore.",
